{"tid":53880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港區人大選舉新增「效忠聲明」　田二少：即係要放棄外國護照","createTime":"2016-12-25T05:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T11:01:12.000Z","uid":11001,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a5697d3f0029f87169802ae761f851e11c8489","tid":53880,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"9月立法會選舉，選舉事務處加入效忠《基本法》確認書，並以此作為取消參選人資格的理由，引起社會廣泛迴響；有份出席北京全國人大常委會會議的港區人大代表馬逢國透露，明年換屆的港區全國人大代表選舉亦將修訂選舉規則，在報名登記表上須聲明效忠中華人民共和國及香港特別行政區，以及擁護憲法和《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n馬逢國認為有關改動與香港近來出現港獨、分離和自決等主張有關，但認為變動對參選人合理，影響不大。另一名人大代表田北辰則指，新增規定<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等於要參選人放棄外國護照</span></span>，因為人大代表等同國會議員，有份選國家主席，絕不能雙重效忠。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161225/56090820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161225%2F56090820&d=n3zzqHPhvY05QAfJB2tZ9ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=9782a111\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161225%2F56090820&h=7edc3d73\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161225/56090820</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YANU12.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYANU12.gif&h=021113e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YANU12.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYANU12.gif&h=021113e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YANU12.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYANU12.gif&h=021113e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"347f604e6a37bff935c1d17070e301ba3faf08d4","tid":53880,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"8da19141f40cd05f83658190981ea6cafef78a07","tid":53880,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:28